          <small>▼</small>
        </button>
        <div class="a">
          NuMeAi is an AI sales assistant that sits on your store and answers customer questions instantly — so you don’t have to. It helps convert “maybe” buyers and works while you sleep.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <button class="q" type="button">
